examples.en: I am bursting to tell you the good news.
The children are bursting out of their clothes so quickly.
The shops are bursting with food.
Shells were bursting all around us.
The storehouses are bursting with goods.
Your mum's bursting with pride for you.
The firemen could enter the burning house only by bursting the door in.
The filing cabinet was full to bursting.
John was bursting with ideas and good humour.
Malaria is bursting out again all over the world.
She responded to the news by bursting into tears.
The enemy are already bursting through our weakened defences.
She was always very enthusiastic and bursting with ideas.
